wiki.summary: Psycho CEO is the first track on the album “2093” by the artist & rapper Yeat. “2093” is the fourth studio album by American rapper Yeat. It was released on February 16, 2024, through Capitol Records, Field Trip Recordings, and Lifestyle Corporation. In this track, Yeat covers his flashy lifestyle, touching on points such as his diamonds, cars, and money. The instrumental of the song has mysterious, futuristic elements which Yeat displays his unique flow on. Read more on Last.fm.
